channel.title: Looking For Coder!
channel.description:
Hello, I am not sure if this is the right spot to post this- if it isnt, could someone please move it? Anyway,
I am looking for a person that can code [b][i]very well.[/i][/b] I want to make a server, but it has to be a different one. No copycats ;D. A webclient or client is fine, or just client.silabsoft.org works as well. I have a lot of ideas for servers. Also, either you or me could be owner/co-owner, I could honestly care less. Either just post here or send me a pm for info :).
P.S. I would prefer you have "aim" or "msn" so we can chat while server is under construction.
Thanks :) -I pwn ur m0m
